 * Creates the PPS Dialog and adds multiple event handlers to interface elements.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * None
 *
 * Return Value:
 * None
 *
 * Example:
 * [] call PPS_fnc_dialogOpen;
 *
 * Public: No
